HEADWORD: Phyllostome
<hw>Phyl"lo*stome</hw> <pr>(f⟦icr⟧l"l⟦osl⟧*st⟦omac⟧m)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Phyllo-</ets> + Gr. <grk>sto`ma</grk>
